Description:
An unparalleled waterside masterpiece! *Book now for your private inspection or video/Facetime tour*
*Book now for your private inspection or video/Facetime tour*
An exceptional Docklands residence that guarantees stunningly spacious living zones, a multitude of alfresco areas, thoughtful custom upgrades, and magnificent 180 degree views. This unparalleled 4 bedroom home over 4 amazing levels is simply unforgettable!
Peacefully positioned towards the end of the Yarras Edge precinct, this luxurious oasis stands alone in terms of its quality and sheer thoughtfulness, with bespoke additions that will make your daily and nightly living an absolute dream.
Ground floor introduces you to 2 generous living zones including a front formal sitting room and an expansive sunken lounge and dining space at the rear with soaring ceilings and a gas log fireplace
Sublime stone kitchen is fitted with the full range of stainless steel Miele appliances while also featuring integrated Electrolux fridge and freezer, butlers pantry, and a wealth of functional storage
Spacious entertainers terrace with built-in BBQ and vertical garden accessed via the front lounge and kitchen
Another large terrace off the lounge/dining room has a northern orientation and superb views of the river and out towards the CBD/Southbank and Bolte Bridge
Master bedroom is an enormous space with a walk-in robe accessed via glass sliding doors, additional BIRs, opulent double vanity spa ensuite with double shower, and north-facing balcony
3 other bedrooms with fitted BIRs easily access a stylish bathroom
Basement home cinema includes bespoke storage plus retractable screen and Epson projector
Top floor features a kitchenette which services another sizeable terrace which has the best west, north, and east views in the entire property
Top floor and ground floor powder rooms
Large climate-controlled wine fridge and an additional wine fridge in the top floor kitchenette
Ducted heating and cooling, floor heating in bathrooms and ensuite, camera security, secure alarm, secure video intercom
Smart centrally controlled zoned lighting system, solar electricity
Lift access to all levels
Secure 4 car basement garage with access to an enormous store room with 2 rainwater tanks
LOCATION
This amazing location is the best of both worlds, where youre away from the buzzing action of the Yarras Edge precinct but close enough to enjoy it when you please. Youre just a short walk to local riverside cafes, restaurants, DFO, South Wharf promenade bars and eateries, Victoria Harbour precinct just over the river, Crown Casino, Port Melbourne and Southbank attractions, and public transport.
Inspect By Appointment

Description:
Highly Sought After Dream Home at 888 Collins, Docklands
When it comes to breathtaking City Skyline view - East Facing, this elegantly appointed and immaculately presented 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom with 1-car space apartment needs to be on the "Must See List" if visiting Docklands precinct.
A rare and exciting opportunity exists to purchase this highly sought after, exclusive apartment at 888 Collins Docklands. Coveted floor plan with commodious master bedroom cum study area with direct access to the small balcony over-looking the water views. The guest room is extremely spacious, light-filled East Facing with superlative City Skyline view, looking out from the large window. Definitely breathtaking views for one to compliment!
Offering first class accommodation, this property amplify its outlook, a modern open floor plan incorporates generous living/dining zone with wide timber flooring and where huge glass aspects facilitate amazing natural light, leading to a spacious balcony overlooking the incredible city skylines. The elegant European kitchen with Miele appliances is all ready for 5 - star cooking.
Additional features include full security access, reverse cycle air-conditioning and secure car parking.
At 888 Collins, it is all about convenience with luxurious resident facilities including a 25-meter indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms and a beautiful communal garden area.
The location is absolutely fabulous with Woolworths Victoria Harbour, Costco, District Docklands, New Quay Restaurants and tram stops all within walking distance.
Please contact Ary Tjin on 0423 891 891 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

The essence of luxurious waterside living
Book now for your private inspection or video/facetime tour.
Tucked away in a tranquil waterside pocket in the highly sought-after Concavo complex from acclaimed architect Bates Smart, this designer 1 bedroom apartment sets the benchmark for luxurious Victoria Harbour precinct living!
·Sitting next to its sister building Convesso, the Concavo complex welcomes you with an opulent lobby and promises an array of amazing resident facilities!
·On the lower 2nd floor for added living convenience
·Perfect for both owner-occupiers and investors
·South-facing orientation allows for wonderful views of the Yarra River from the undercover balcony
·Spacious living/meals also with views further includes the gorgeous stone kitchen with eye-catching splashback and Blanco appliances including an induction cooktop
·Bedroom is complete with mirrored built-in robe storage
·Impressive bathroom features first class fittings and a European laundry
·Ducted heating and cooling
·Smart pad video intercom with additional energy monitoring features
·Storage cage
·Secure car space
Watch our Facebook Live Tour - https://bit.ly/2LOaqkt
AMENITIES
Residents of the Concavo complex will have access to a 24 hour concierge, communal lounge, business centre and board room, indoor cinema, north-facing sky garden with BBQ facilities, 25m indoor heated pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, and treatment room. The Concavo building also has a 5 star energy rating, which is the only residential development in the Docklands to achieve this status.
LOCATION
The Victoria Harbour precinct is a wonderful mix of retail and office spaces making it ideal for those who work in the area or the nearby CBD. The Concavo building is located right next to Buluk Park and the Library @ The Dock, while youre also moments to Bourke Street cafes and restaurants, Woolworths Victoria Harbour, Marvel Stadium, The Hub @ Docklands, Docklands Sports Courts, and trams.

Description:
Seize this opportunity to capitalise on this one time only offer! Call now to inspect!
Designed by the award-winning Bates Smart, the Marina Homes are one of a kind with only 17 within this exclusive development. You will be the envy of all your friends and family as there is nothing else like this in Melbourne, so capitalise on this golden opportunity to come and visit this stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home that showcases a blend of captivating, gallery-inspired spaces and uninterrupted north-facing Victoria Harbour views which can never be built out! Led by luxury over an impressive 256m2 (approx.), the breathtaking panorama views are shared in all balcony-accessed bedrooms.
One of the most important and unique key features is the security of the premises. You not only have a 24 hour concierge service, but remote entry access through the security garage on the side of the Convesso complex, which leads you straight through the communal carpark and up to your very own private double lock up garage and storage room. No lifts, no foyer, just straight through to your front door. In this development there is only 3 private residences per floor, along with a private lift that will get you up to your residence if choose to go through the foyer of the complex.
You'll feel a homely sense of relaxation as soon as you enter your front door, with stylish warm oak flooring sweeping across the free-flowing living and dining spaces which are flooded with natural northern light. This seamless stone-finished kitchen is fully equipped with top-of-the-range De Dietrich and Liebherr appliances not to mention the benefit of a concealed butler's pantry effortlessly handling all the demands of the multiple dinner parties you can host or your New Year's Eve fireworks social gatherings.
Alfresco entertaining in summer will be effortless with this full-width balcony, not to mention the stunning views overlooking Melbourne city, Marvel Stadium, Victoria Harbour, stretching across to the Bolte Bridge. Who wouldn't want to look out to these 180 degree views on a daily basis!
Other key features include full C-Bus-driven home automation, ducted heating/cooling, a handy powder room, study alcove, double glazing, remote-controlled curtains and block-out blinds, and panel-controlled, outdoor strip heating.

Description:
Waterfront Brilliance in Array Complex
A rare offering, this luxurious North-facing 3 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom waterfront apartment offers space, style and panoramic views in Mirvac's recently completed 'Array' complex.
Sensational uninterrupted city skyline and water views are showcased from the 270-degree wraparound balcony, the covered terrace area and the floor to ceiling feature glass windows.
Cleverly designed open floor plan offers zoned living and includes designated areas for dining, entertaining family living.
The gourmet kitchen features stone bench tops, glass splashback, island bench/breakfast bar, Hettich drawers and a full complement of Miele appliances including two conventional ovens and a dishwasher.
The master bedroom, with bay vistas, boasts full double vanity en-suite bathroom with freestanding bath, while the other bedrooms come with BIRs have convenient access to the central bathroom.
Enjoy the use of the on-site gymnasium, concierge, residents lounge and access to the 'RekDek' fitness centre, which including pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Convenient location is close to a selection of South Wharf eateries, Crown Casino and the Yarra River walking paths, Etihad Stadium and the DFO Shopping precinct. Transport options include Southern Cross Railway Station, easy freeway access and Melbourne's infamous trams, which provide instant access to the CBD.

If you're attending an inspection, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. Description:
Stylish Docklands Living at The Quays
Absolutely amazing City Views from both of bedroom and balcony suited on 16th floor.
Walk to Etihad Stadium, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Newquay Promenade and Victoria Harbour, city shops and nightlife, trams, & Southern Cross Station. Not mention the free tram just on your step.
Bright full windows allow for sensational natural light through the spacious main living and dining hub, while the adjoining stone kitchen with s/steel appliances makes preparing nightly dinners just too easy.
Both bedrooms have BIRs and are separated by the living zone for privacy, while at the front of the apartment is the luxury bathroom with vibrant mosaic tiles and large shower. Other extras are the balcony with stunning views, laundry facilities, reverse cycle cooling (in both bedrooms), intercom entry, and a secure undercover car park on the title.
Sports Facilities include: indoor 25 metre pool, sauna, gym and the only residential complex in Docklands with a tennis court. Others amenities include a private lounge, cinema, library and well-manicured landscape gardened BBQ area.
Vacant possession is available now, previous rental income is $550/week. This apartment is absolutely perfect for a professional looking for a quiet city pad or if youre a first home buyer looking for that first property thats so hard to find and decide on!
Vendor says sell it. It wouldn't be long on the market. Call Stephen your CBD expert on 0468 955 586 to arrange the inspection.

**BY APPOINTMENT ONLY. PLEASE CONTACT AGENT TO ARRANGE** An Apartment Gem, A Cut Above The Rest.
Brilliant North facing apartment nestled in the Aqui Promenade residential complex, designed by award winning architects Woods Bagot.
Located on the 3rd floor, this spacious 1 bedroom has so much to offer.
Open plan dining and living area adjoins a fantastic undercover glass balustrade balcony perfect for relaxing.
Modern galley kitchen with integrated stainless steel Miele appliances including gas stove top and oven. Plenty of storage space highlighted by the white cabinetry and timber accented feature panelling
Stylish bedroom with mirrored built in robes, also with floor to ceiling windows and a study nook.

Complex features include: 25m swimming pool, gymnasium, onsite manager, security entrance, business/study meeting area, communal BBQ and landscaped rooftop garden.
Located close to District Docklands shopping precinct, Hoyts Cinema, the newly opened Woolworths and Dan Murphy's. O'Brien ice rink and Ron Barassi Snr park is also very close by.
Free tram zoned, close to Southern Cross Station, and easy access to the freeway system.
Enjoy the many facets that the area offers.

Description:
Excellent investment opportunity at the Lacrosse
Located in a prime position where Docklands Meets the CBD, is this immaculately presented & spacious apartment in the Lacrosse complex. Welcoming ample natural light from an East-facing balcony & being only minutes away from everything the city has to offer, this apartment incorporates a perfect blend convenience & style.
The apartment is extremely well lit from dawn until dusk, with floor to ceiling windows throughout the living & dining zone. Featuring a well- appointed galley kitchen with stone bench tops, glass splash backs & stainless-steel appliances. A generously sized bedroom with built in robes & ample storage space. A stylish & sleek central bathroom with floor to ceiling tiles and high-end fittings.
Other features include European Laundry, reverse-cycle heating & cooling unit & double-glazed windows. Building amenities include fully equipped gymnasium, pool, private lift access, secure video-intercom entry & bicycle storage.
In a stunning Location just footsteps away from Melbourne's lively CBD, this residence offers the benefits of city-fringe living without the commute. The vibrant Docklands Promenade restaurants & bars, Etihad stadium, Harbour town Shopping Centre & Southern Cross train station all only a short walk away, as well as a variety of CBD attractions. With transport options everywhere & trams right at your doorstep, this apartment is an excellent investment opportunity or entry-level home !

Description:
Stunning brand new apartment of Marina Tower Docklands
Complete and ready to move into this one bedroom at Marina Tower on level 4, and priced to sell!
Sale via nomination, save on the off the plan stamp duty as per the original 2015 contract.
Magnificently designed by award-winning architects DKO and perfectly framed by expansive city, Port Phillip Bay and Victorian mountain views, this landmark tower heralds a new standard of Melbourne living. Beautifully encased by a shimmering façade meticulous interiors and fittings.
Meticulously designed and individually tailored, each apartment is beautifully fitted with a superior level of specification and the highest attention to detail. Light, airy and contemporary, the interiors capture breathtaking, panoramic views towards the city, bay and mountain ranges, through floor-to-ceiling glazing that also encapsulates private balconies to retreat to each day.
This very special property is perfectly positioned as a gateway to Melbournes best fashion, arts, culinary and sporting activities, with easy access by water taxi or free city tram. Open your front door to a world of amenity on the ground floor; including relaxing gardens, artisan coffee from our café, à la carte dining, and laneway access to New Quay Square. The level seven rooftop creates an unparalleled experience for entertaining, dining and relaxing with a range of amenity surrounded by lush gardens for residents to enjoy exclusively. Unfolding as a rich, sophisticated series of spaces available exclusively to residents, The Marina Club offers a range of entertaining amenity in absolute style and with effortless luxury.

Description:
Unmatched Penthouse Living with almost 360 Degree Views!
Note: Inspections via private appointment only. Please register for a private viewing.
Enjoying a wonderful penthouse location on the 30th floor of the high end 'Forge' complex, this spacious, light-filled, and opulent 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment is the pinnacle of luxurious Wharf's Entrance living with almost 360 degree views that are some of the best in Melbourne.
A shining jewel in one of the Dockland's most exclusive buildings, this immaculate and utterly sublime residence presents as new while enjoying high end fittings and fixtures as well as high ceilings which gives you a genuine feeling of spaciousness. The central living zone is as good as it gets when it comes to light, space, and views, with this area split into the dedicated dining area with curved windows which looks out to Port Phillip Bay, while the lounge also enjoys wonderful views to the west along with warming afternoon sun.
Separating the lounge and dining zones is the deluxe stone kitchen equipped with a waterfall island bench, soft-closing drawers, stainless steel Smeg appliances, and integrated Fisher & Paykel fridge and freezer. An enclosed balcony terrace with louvre windows has a brilliant northern orientation which allows for memorable views of the mountain ranges, Victoria Harbour, Marvel Stadium, and the CBD.
The master bedroom delivers ample BIRs and a pristine double vanity ensuite, while 2 other bedrooms with bay views have BIRs including one of these bedrooms which features a sizeable study space. Other penthouse extras include a stylish bathroom, separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure video intercom, storage cage, and 2 secure car spaces.
Residents of the building also have access to a private dining room and cinema with cityscape views, state of the art health and well-being facility called the 'Wharf Club' which features a gym and pool, and a café overlooking the water as well as the Wharf's Landing Park. You're also positioned not far from South Wharf Promenade with a range of bars and restaurants, DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Port Melbourne and South Melbourne attractions, public transport, and Westgate Freeway.
